WEBVTT

00:00:04.640 --> 00:00:07.040
(Previously)
There's one rule of mine you should know.

00:00:07.560 --> 00:00:08.560
I don't…

00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:10.119
do “seconds.”

00:00:10.120 --> 00:00:12.200
but I think it was too fast.

00:00:12.760 --> 00:00:15.360
Who told you… that I like him?

00:00:15.960 --> 00:00:16.960
Jimmy did.

00:00:17.200 --> 00:00:19.200
Did you tell P'Toh that I like Fah?

00:00:19.560 --> 00:00:21.400
Something felt off back at the resort.

00:00:22.440 --> 00:00:24.160
You started this game, Teh.

00:00:24.400 --> 00:00:25.840
Can you drop the…

00:00:26.160 --> 00:00:27.520
“no seconds” rule?

00:00:27.680 --> 00:00:29.560
But I'm a man of my word.

00:00:29.760 --> 00:00:30.760
But every rule…

00:00:30.920 --> 00:00:32.280
has an exception.

00:00:32.880 --> 00:00:34.520
I want them to have a partner.

00:04:52.240 --> 00:04:53.320
May I?

00:04:57.120 --> 00:04:59.480
Please don't hurt me.

00:05:26.880 --> 00:05:28.400
I would never.

00:05:30.960 --> 00:05:32.680
You're too precious...

00:05:34.720 --> 00:05:35.800
And yet...

00:05:42.560 --> 00:05:43.840
so tempting to break.

00:05:48.680 --> 00:05:51.480
Then… break me. I'm yours.

00:05:55.080 --> 00:05:56.560
I'll be gentle with you.

00:08:35.000 --> 00:08:38.000
"Love Alert"
(Episode 4)

00:09:16.360 --> 00:09:17.400
You're cute.

00:10:37.720 --> 00:10:38.920
What's that sound?

00:10:41.400 --> 00:10:42.480
Just a message.

00:10:44.200 --> 00:10:45.920
Who's texting you this early?

00:10:49.120 --> 00:10:50.160
It's Jimmy.

00:10:57.000 --> 00:10:58.640
Can't we cuddle a bit longer?

00:11:02.280 --> 00:11:04.080
I need to step out for a bit.

00:11:05.080 --> 00:11:06.800
And I'll give you more than just a hug.

00:11:53.640 --> 00:11:54.840
Bastard!

00:12:16.320 --> 00:12:17.920
What the hell did you do to my brother?!

00:12:18.400 --> 00:12:21.560
Are the photos not clear enough?
Or do you want the full video?

00:12:22.040 --> 00:12:23.400
God damn you!

00:12:23.600 --> 00:12:25.120
It's good that you're mad, Teh.

00:12:25.640 --> 00:12:28.880
Now you know how I felt

00:12:30.320 --> 00:12:33.560
when you were screwing Fah next to me.

00:12:35.520 --> 00:12:37.240
You stabbed me in the back.

00:12:38.000 --> 00:12:41.520
You knew I like Fah, but you still did it.

00:12:43.000 --> 00:12:45.120
But this has nothing to do with P'Toh.

00:12:46.240 --> 00:12:48.120
I've made it his business now.

00:12:51.960 --> 00:12:53.560
Stay away from Fah,

00:12:56.000 --> 00:12:57.520
and I'll leave your brother alone.

00:12:59.720 --> 00:13:04.040
Even if I leave him,
You'll never have a chance with him anyway.

00:13:05.720 --> 00:13:07.000
End it or not?

00:13:18.320 --> 00:13:20.080
I won't let you hurt my brother!

00:13:20.880 --> 00:13:22.480
I'll stay away from Fah.

00:13:23.640 --> 00:13:25.320
You'd better keep your word.

00:13:28.000 --> 00:13:29.920
Otherwise, I'll keep using your brother…

00:13:32.280 --> 00:13:33.280
until I'm bored.

00:13:34.440 --> 00:13:35.720
Then I'll throw him back to you.

00:13:35.960 --> 00:13:39.080
My brother is a human being!

00:13:39.360 --> 00:13:41.560
How can you be such a cold-blooded...

00:13:43.160 --> 00:13:44.160
Son of a bitch!

00:14:57.440 --> 00:14:59.040
Stay away from Fah,

00:14:59.840 --> 00:15:01.280
and I'll leave your brother alone.

00:15:02.760 --> 00:15:04.360
You'd better keep your word.

00:15:04.960 --> 00:15:06.600
Otherwise, I'll keep using your brother…

00:15:07.040 --> 00:15:09.600
until I'm bored.
Then I'll throw him back to you.

00:15:28.080 --> 00:15:30.400
P'Toh, what's that burning smell?

00:15:36.920 --> 00:15:38.880
Well, I…

00:15:39.040 --> 00:15:40.520
wanted the egg to be crispy.

00:15:44.280 --> 00:15:45.680
Can I have mine like that too?

00:15:49.520 --> 00:15:50.520
Please?

00:16:17.080 --> 00:16:18.080
P'Toh,

00:16:19.040 --> 00:16:20.200
what's your secret?

00:16:20.920 --> 00:16:22.640
I've never had a fried egg this good.

00:16:24.960 --> 00:16:26.000
There's no secret.

00:16:27.280 --> 00:16:30.640
I just… want the person
eating it to be happy.

00:16:31.240 --> 00:16:32.440
That's why it turned out well.

00:16:33.760 --> 00:16:34.760
I see.

00:16:35.800 --> 00:16:36.800
You see what?

00:16:39.080 --> 00:16:42.640
You wanted me to be happy.
That's why it's so good.

00:16:46.720 --> 00:16:47.760
Now that you know.

00:16:50.720 --> 00:16:52.960
I hope you'll do the same for me.

00:16:54.040 --> 00:16:55.160
Or at least…

00:16:56.800 --> 00:16:58.320
please don't hurt me.

00:17:01.320 --> 00:17:02.480
Why say that?

00:17:03.640 --> 00:17:05.320
Was I too rough on you last night?

00:17:09.120 --> 00:17:10.720
You were my first.

00:17:14.200 --> 00:17:15.200
P'Toh,

00:17:17.880 --> 00:17:19.840
do you know how important a “first” is?

00:17:21.760 --> 00:17:22.760
How?

00:17:26.080 --> 00:17:27.920
You can have as many people as you want,

00:17:29.600 --> 00:17:33.080
But you only ever… have one “first.”

00:17:43.840 --> 00:17:45.600
And I'm so glad …

00:17:47.160 --> 00:17:48.640
that it was me.

00:17:57.360 --> 00:17:59.800
I guess I'm not your first, right?

00:18:05.480 --> 00:18:07.000
I don't really care about that.

00:18:08.440 --> 00:18:09.640
Because I'd…

00:18:12.720 --> 00:18:15.080
rather be your “only one.”

00:18:32.040 --> 00:18:33.040
P'Toh,

00:18:33.800 --> 00:18:37.440
thanks for everything. For the fried egg…

00:18:38.480 --> 00:18:39.720
and for youself.

00:18:41.680 --> 00:18:45.680
Anyway, I have to head to class.

00:19:40.080 --> 00:19:42.760
Get it over with. I'm gonna be late.

00:19:44.520 --> 00:19:46.599
Punch me! Do it if you have the balls!

00:19:46.600 --> 00:19:47.640
You bastard!

00:19:50.600 --> 00:19:53.440
You're even worse.

00:20:01.400 --> 00:20:05.800
I hope this is the last time
I see you near my brother.

00:20:08.760 --> 00:20:11.000
I expect the same from you…

00:20:12.240 --> 00:20:13.400
Stay away from Fah.

00:20:15.400 --> 00:20:16.400
Fine,

00:20:17.440 --> 00:20:18.520
I can do it.

00:20:19.960 --> 00:20:21.640
Keep your end of the deal too,

00:20:23.600 --> 00:20:25.400
or I'll beat you up.

00:20:34.200 --> 00:20:35.200
Oh.

00:20:36.840 --> 00:20:39.760
If you don't want your brother
suicidal from a broken heart,

00:20:40.240 --> 00:20:41.680
you'd better not be all talk.

00:20:46.840 --> 00:20:48.920
See you later, “bestie.”

00:21:14.240 --> 00:21:16.760
How long have you been standing there?

00:21:18.720 --> 00:21:21.320
Oh, Teh. You're home.

00:21:25.440 --> 00:21:26.880
Why are you looking at me like that?

00:21:32.280 --> 00:21:33.320
P'Toh…

00:21:34.360 --> 00:21:36.240
I'm telling you again.

00:21:36.640 --> 00:21:40.720
Jimmy's a player who's
incapable of loving anyone.

00:21:43.000 --> 00:21:45.320
Why do you keep bringing it up?

00:21:46.240 --> 00:21:48.040
I wanna keep reminding you,

00:21:48.600 --> 00:21:50.120
so you don't fall for him.

00:21:54.080 --> 00:21:55.360
I'm just worried about you.

00:23:57.320 --> 00:23:58.600
You've got this, Toh.

00:24:00.480 --> 00:24:01.720
Stay strong.

00:24:02.960 --> 00:24:04.720
You can make him love you for real.

00:24:55.000 --> 00:24:58.440
Then break me. I'm yours.

00:25:19.080 --> 00:25:20.080
Fah!

00:25:22.080 --> 00:25:23.080
Teh.

00:25:40.960 --> 00:25:42.560
It's about our date tonight.

00:25:43.440 --> 00:25:46.600
I already booked movie tickets,
but drinks are on you. Deal?

00:26:02.360 --> 00:26:04.400
I can't… I have to study.

00:26:06.640 --> 00:26:09.200
Oh. What about another day?

00:26:09.680 --> 00:26:12.720
But you're paying for tickets and drinks.

00:26:13.480 --> 00:26:14.480
Name a day.

00:26:16.040 --> 00:26:17.800
I don't know… Maybe after exams.

00:26:18.920 --> 00:26:19.920
And when is that?

00:26:22.360 --> 00:26:24.000
The professor hasn't announced the dates.

00:26:25.880 --> 00:26:27.440
You should invite someone else.

00:26:28.440 --> 00:26:32.680
You really want to watch this movie, right?
Do it before it out of theathers.

00:26:33.640 --> 00:26:35.080
- But...
- I need to go to class.

00:26:35.760 --> 00:26:36.760
Let's talk later.

00:26:50.640 --> 00:26:51.840
Fah.

00:26:52.520 --> 00:26:55.080
Oh, Jimmy. What's up?

00:26:55.880 --> 00:26:58.160
I… accidentally bought
an extra movie ticket.

00:27:01.120 --> 00:27:03.840
Everyone's talking about it.
Want to go with me?

00:27:04.720 --> 00:27:06.200
I want to see that one.

00:27:07.240 --> 00:27:09.440
But… you should find someone else.

00:27:11.240 --> 00:27:12.240
Thanks anyway.

00:27:12.360 --> 00:27:14.680
Why? You don't want to go with me?

00:27:15.120 --> 00:27:16.120
Nope.

00:27:18.040 --> 00:27:20.800
I already have someone specific in mind.

00:27:21.720 --> 00:27:26.080
Besides, you're a hot shot.
You'll find a date in no time.

00:27:41.560 --> 00:27:42.880
You only want Teh, don't you?

00:27:58.840 --> 00:27:59.280
Hello?

00:27:59.640 --> 00:28:02.400
Mr. Jimmy! Saensee's been hit by a car!

00:28:02.520 --> 00:28:03.520
What?!

00:28:08.920 --> 00:28:11.560
Jimmy, what happened? Tell me.

00:28:13.400 --> 00:28:15.320
Saensee, my cat, he's been hit.

00:28:16.160 --> 00:28:17.720
How… is he now?

00:28:18.720 --> 00:28:21.480
I don't know. A vet is examining him.

00:28:29.080 --> 00:28:33.040
P'Toh, what am I going
to do if he doesn't make it?

00:28:41.200 --> 00:28:42.200
P'Toh,

00:28:43.880 --> 00:28:44.920
I'm so sorry…

00:28:45.760 --> 00:28:48.800
I didn't know who else
to call, so I called you.

00:28:51.360 --> 00:28:52.360
It's okay.

00:28:53.160 --> 00:28:54.160
Take a deep breath.

00:28:57.200 --> 00:28:58.200
Sit down.

00:29:00.080 --> 00:29:01.600
Will Saensee be okay?

00:29:08.440 --> 00:29:09.440
Take it easy.

00:29:17.040 --> 00:29:21.240
Don't worry so much, Jimmy.
The vet said Saensee's going to be fine.

00:29:22.520 --> 00:29:23.880
He wasn't hit by the car.

00:29:25.440 --> 00:29:26.760
He was just in shock.

00:29:28.720 --> 00:29:31.320
He's in good hands tonight. Don't worry.

00:29:38.480 --> 00:29:39.480
I know.

00:29:40.600 --> 00:29:41.840
I can't help being worried.

00:29:43.240 --> 00:29:48.400
We normally cuddle on the bed.
It's just me and him.

00:29:56.800 --> 00:29:59.440
Let Saensee cuddle
with the vet for tonight.

00:30:00.840 --> 00:30:03.760
If anything happens, the vet's right there.

00:30:05.360 --> 00:30:11.160
If Saensee is ready to come home,
I'll go with you and pick him up. Deal?

00:30:25.400 --> 00:30:26.760
Thank you so much, P'Toh.

00:30:29.200 --> 00:30:31.000
I don't know how to thank you.

00:30:33.000 --> 00:30:35.040
I would've been a mess if you weren't…

00:30:36.520 --> 00:30:37.520
here by my side.

00:30:40.760 --> 00:30:41.880
Don't mention it.

00:30:43.040 --> 00:30:45.360
Just let me know if you need anything.

00:30:46.040 --> 00:30:48.720
We're not exactly strangers.

00:31:03.000 --> 00:31:04.520
Thank you so much.

00:31:31.480 --> 00:31:33.080
Mmm, smells so good.

00:31:34.760 --> 00:31:37.720
Which one? The cabonara or me?

00:31:42.920 --> 00:31:46.440
Both the chef and the meal.

00:31:50.840 --> 00:31:53.680
I'm all sweaty. Stop sniffing me.

00:32:02.960 --> 00:32:05.240
I don't smell any sweat. You smell nice.

00:32:06.680 --> 00:32:08.440
You're teasing me again.

00:32:11.960 --> 00:32:13.440
You're just so fun to tease.

00:32:18.640 --> 00:32:19.640
I thank you for…

00:32:20.760 --> 00:32:21.760
being here with me.

00:32:27.320 --> 00:32:28.400
I'll plate this.

00:32:39.480 --> 00:32:44.000
Put it on the plates for me.
I need to take this call.

00:32:57.360 --> 00:32:58.360
Yes, Teh?

00:32:58.680 --> 00:33:00.120
Where are you?

00:33:00.840 --> 00:33:02.400
Why aren't you home yet?

00:33:03.360 --> 00:33:09.280
Oh, I'm… out with my friend…
Someone who just got back from the US.

00:33:09.600 --> 00:33:10.640
What's up?

00:33:13.320 --> 00:33:14.440
I'm just worried.

00:33:15.040 --> 00:33:17.960
It's already late. When
are you coming back?

00:33:18.440 --> 00:33:21.800
Come on, I'm a grown-up.
Let me have some space.

00:33:22.960 --> 00:33:26.520
How can I? You'll run into bad people.

00:33:30.720 --> 00:33:32.560
By the way…

00:33:34.640 --> 00:33:36.320
has Jimmy contacted you?

00:33:38.160 --> 00:33:39.800
Ah…

00:33:42.120 --> 00:33:43.120
No.

00:33:43.960 --> 00:33:44.960
Why?

00:33:46.640 --> 00:33:47.640
Nothing.

00:33:48.760 --> 00:33:49.800
That's it.

00:33:51.120 --> 00:33:52.720
Just get home soon.

00:33:52.960 --> 00:33:54.520
Got it, young master.

00:34:12.040 --> 00:34:15.160
(Get well soon, Saensee.)

00:34:27.360 --> 00:34:29.240
I didn't know I was living in the US.

00:34:31.720 --> 00:34:32.880
You heard that?

00:34:33.680 --> 00:34:35.120
I thought I was being quiet.

00:34:37.080 --> 00:34:38.080
Well…

00:34:38.680 --> 00:34:41.960
I lied because I didn't want Teh to worry.

00:34:46.400 --> 00:34:49.240
You said you were out with your “friend”…

00:34:52.600 --> 00:34:54.120
Stay the night.

00:34:57.320 --> 00:34:59.520
So I can hug you in Saensee's stead.

00:35:01.840 --> 00:35:02.840
But I...

00:35:02.841 --> 00:35:04.000
Please.

00:35:05.200 --> 00:35:07.280
- But I...
- Please.

00:35:07.920 --> 00:35:09.000
Just one night.

00:35:11.360 --> 00:35:12.559
Jim, I must...

00:35:12.560 --> 00:35:13.560
P'Toh,

00:35:17.440 --> 00:35:18.560
Stay with me.

00:35:36.080 --> 00:35:37.080
Jimmy?

00:35:37.680 --> 00:35:38.840
When did you get in here?

00:35:39.840 --> 00:35:40.920
Just now.

00:35:43.560 --> 00:35:45.560
Let me help you wash up.

00:38:14.240 --> 00:38:15.480
(Plaifah: You up?)

00:38:27.320 --> 00:38:29.480
(Plaifah: I thought you said
you wanted to pursue me?)

00:38:30.000 --> 00:38:32.560
(If you've changed your
mind, just be direct about it.)

00:38:34.960 --> 00:38:36.560
It's not like I want to quit.

00:38:54.520 --> 00:39:00.480
(Read)

00:39:05.720 --> 00:39:07.280
What's with him?

00:39:09.360 --> 00:39:10.360
He didn't reply.

00:39:15.880 --> 00:39:16.880
Did he…

00:39:19.560 --> 00:39:20.800
have a fight with P'Toh?

00:39:37.360 --> 00:39:38.360
Who's calling?

00:39:39.480 --> 00:39:40.480
Oh,

00:39:40.840 --> 00:39:41.840
it's Fah.

00:39:46.080 --> 00:39:47.840
You're not going to answer him?

00:39:50.280 --> 00:39:51.960
He probably called me to ask where I am.

00:39:53.040 --> 00:39:56.000
I'm afraid if I keep
lying, Teh will catch on.

00:40:05.920 --> 00:40:07.160
He didn't pick up.

00:40:25.400 --> 00:40:26.400
You're cute.

00:40:28.320 --> 00:40:29.720
You're that scared of your brother.

00:40:33.760 --> 00:40:35.040
It's your fault.

00:40:36.000 --> 00:40:37.640
You're making me a liar.

00:40:39.240 --> 00:40:40.800
Is a lie for your peace of mind…

00:40:41.680 --> 00:40:42.680
wrong?

00:40:52.280 --> 00:40:53.280
And…

00:40:53.960 --> 00:40:55.840
have you ever lied to me?

00:41:00.160 --> 00:41:01.600
What would I even have to lie about?

00:41:04.240 --> 00:41:05.240
I don't know.

00:41:05.760 --> 00:41:07.720
I was… just wondering.

00:41:10.520 --> 00:41:11.520
I hope…

00:41:12.200 --> 00:41:14.440
you won't hurt me.

00:41:18.840 --> 00:41:20.400
Don't be cruel to me.

00:41:54.080 --> 00:41:57.880
Hello there! I'm all better now!

00:41:58.200 --> 00:42:00.480
Strong and healthy as ever!

00:42:03.320 --> 00:42:05.480
Glad to see you're okay, Saensee.

00:42:08.920 --> 00:42:11.680
Feeling great and ready to go!

00:42:12.600 --> 00:42:14.240
Stay healthy, okay?

00:42:18.240 --> 00:42:20.120
There you go, into the bag you go.

00:42:26.240 --> 00:42:27.240
Hello?

00:42:28.120 --> 00:42:29.400
Got it. I'll be there.

00:42:31.640 --> 00:42:32.640
P'Toh,

00:42:33.080 --> 00:42:37.120
I have to rush to uni.
Can you take Saensee back to the condo?

00:42:38.880 --> 00:42:39.880
Of course.

00:42:48.320 --> 00:42:51.680
Stay with mama for now.
Daddy will be home soon.

00:42:58.720 --> 00:42:59.720
See you later.

00:43:33.200 --> 00:43:36.480
P'Toh didn't come home last night.
Where did you take him?

00:43:37.720 --> 00:43:41.360
Saensee got hit by a car and
was admitted. How should I know?

00:43:42.680 --> 00:43:43.680
Bull.

00:43:44.600 --> 00:43:47.720
Believe what you want.
I need to go check on Saensee now.

00:43:47.960 --> 00:43:49.720
Are you sure you're
staying away from P'Toh?

00:43:50.520 --> 00:43:51.520
Yeah.

00:43:53.720 --> 00:43:54.720
What about you?

00:43:56.240 --> 00:43:57.560
Stay away from Fah?

00:43:59.120 --> 00:44:00.880
I've stayed away from him.

00:44:08.640 --> 00:44:11.200
How's… Saensee?

00:44:15.400 --> 00:44:16.920
A vet said it was just shock

00:44:17.920 --> 00:44:20.080
and had to stay overnight for observation.

00:44:21.120 --> 00:44:22.120
Good.

00:44:23.080 --> 00:44:24.880
I'm glad it's nothing serious.

00:44:32.320 --> 00:44:34.520
There you are. I've been looking for you.

00:44:39.920 --> 00:44:41.120
Are you free, Jimmy?

00:44:45.400 --> 00:44:46.480
Come with me for a bit?

00:44:52.800 --> 00:44:53.800
Sure thing.

00:45:14.240 --> 00:45:15.280
P'Toh…

00:45:17.240 --> 00:45:18.920
Has Jimmy contacted you?

00:45:20.760 --> 00:45:22.360
Ah…

00:45:24.720 --> 00:45:25.720
No.

00:45:26.600 --> 00:45:27.640
Why?

00:45:30.560 --> 00:45:33.160
(Get well soon, Saensee.)

00:45:37.840 --> 00:45:40.840
(Get well soon, Saensee.)

00:45:45.120 --> 00:45:46.840
You're not on my level, Teh.

00:45:50.920 --> 00:45:52.416
(Next Episode)
Are you here to spy on me now?

00:45:52.440 --> 00:45:54.320
I couldn't get a hold of you.

00:45:55.280 --> 00:45:57.360
Don't call me. And don't come
here again for a while.

00:46:02.600 --> 00:46:06.319
Are you spacing out?
Don't tell me you miss Jimmy.

00:46:06.320 --> 00:46:07.760
Are you in love with Jimmy?

00:46:08.120 --> 00:46:10.000
There's really nothing between us, I swear.

00:46:10.520 --> 00:46:12.520
It's fine if you don't
want to tell me the truth.